'''Herdis von Magnus''' (23 September 1912 – 15 March 1992) was a renowned Danish [[polio]] expert who once worked with [[Jonas Salk]], following which she directed the first Danish [[polio vaccination]] programme with her husband [[Preben von Magnus]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://denstoredanske.dk/Dansk_Biografisk_Leksikon/Sundhed/L%25C3%25A6ge/Herdis_von_Magnus |title=Herdis von Magnus |website=Gyldendal - Den Store Danske |language=da |access-date=2018-10-17}}</ref> She also worked on [[encephalitis]].<ref name="Seytre200">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=wV3AEICQ8eQC&pg=PA76&dq=Preben+von+Magnus+salk&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjbmZyUkdvdAhXMxIUKHQAXDUMQ6AEIMzAC#v=onepage&q=Preben%20von%20Magnus%20salk&f=false|title=The Death of a Disease: A History of the Eradication of Poliomyelitis|last=Seytre|first=Bernard|last2=Shaffer|first2=Mary|date=2004|publisher=Rutgers University Press|year=|isbn=9780813536767|location=|pages=76|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Jacobs2015">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=kCp-BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA181&dq=Preben+von+Magnus&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjAy5rmi9vdAhVDaBoKHURkAu8Q6AEILDAB#v=onepage&q=Preben%20von%20Magnus&f=false|title=Jonas Salk: A Life|last=Jacobs|first=Charlotte DeCroes|last2=Jacobs|first2=Charlotte|date=2015|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=|isbn=9780199334414|location=|pages=181|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=mZVuDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA141&lpg=PA141&dq=Herdis+von+Magnus&source=bl&ots=jXMoTGAC68&sig=gqsLPcRNuMc9RALCFLRumB4-8eY&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwil-dfkw9vdAhXNa8AKHZuKDeQ4ChDoATABegQIBxAB#v=onepage&q=Herdis%20von%20Magnus&f=false|title=Polio Across the Iron Curtain: Hungary's Cold War with an Epidemic|last=Vargha|first=Dóra|date=|publisher=Cambridge University Press|year=2018|isbn=9781108431019|location=|pages=141|language=en}}</ref>
